::KitKat::

She motioned for Destructor to follow her as she left the bridge and 
headed to the lab.  "I don't want Black Aracnia to see any of this.  
We may talk, but then again, that is all we may do.  I don't trust 
her eyt.  Something isn't right and I don't know what it is.  But I 
am going to find out.  I will have to admit, the thought of joing up 
and getting Megatron is very appealing." She walked towards the labs, 
smiling.
